In a small saucepan, cook BACARDI(R) Limon over medium-high heat until reduced by half. Place bananas, butter, jalapeno pepper and salt into a blender along with the reduced BACARDI(R) Limn and pure for 40 seconds until smooth. Set the sauce aside and keep it warm. Halibut Directions: Season the halibut fillets with salt and pepper. Lightly coat the skin side of each fillet with butter. Grill the fillets skin side down for 2-3 minutes. Turn fillets over and continue cooking to desired doneness. Place fillets on plates, spoon sauce on each fillet and garnish with fresh cilantro sprigs. Serve immediately.